{
  "version": 2,
  "name": "Star Field",
  "description": "Star Field — fully atomized from the legacy `node.star_field_2d` Rust bundle. Composed entirely of existing texture-domain atoms: `voronoi_2d` (per-cell distance + hash) → `scale_offset` (invert distance) → `power_texture` (spike to star core, exponent driven by Size slider) → `channel_mix` (R→RGB, white stars) → in parallel: `channel_mix` (swizzle voronoi.A cell_hash → R) → `smoothstep_texture` (density threshold) → `mix(Multiply)` mask the core → `trig_texture` (per-pixel sin with per-cell freq/phase via texture-shadow inputs) → `mix(Multiply)` apply twinkle → final brightness.\n\nThe voronoi `offset_x` / `offset_y` are the sum of `drift_t × drift_x` (animation) AND `-0.5 × scale` (centering) — so when the user moves the Scale slider, the cell grid expands from the canvas center rather than from the top-left.\n\nKey primitive enablers from the original decomposition (2026-05-27):\n(1) `node.voronoi_2d` exposes the F1-winner cell hash on the A channel — was constant 1.0, now drives per-cell variation across the cellular-noise family (foam, cracked glass, embers, tiles, stars). Each cell's hash is decorrelated from its jitter offset so it stays deterministic as jitter animates.\n(2) `node.channel_mix` GPU shader implemented (was a no-op stub) — completes the 4×4 RGBA matrix transform. Used in two places here: swizzle voronoi.A → R for cell-hash reading, and broadcast R → RGB to make the star core white instead of single-channel red.\n(3) `node.trig_texture` extended with optional `freq_tex` / `phase_tex` texture-shadow inputs — per-pixel freq/phase from texture R channel when wired, unlocks per-cell unique twinkle (each cell pulses at its own freq + phase, not just a global LFO).\n(4) Tuning pass: `node.power_texture` extended with port-shadow on `exponent` so the Size slider can drive star spike sharpness via an inverting `affine_scalar` (slider 0 → exp=30 tight, slider 1 → exp=2 big halo).\n\nDropped from the legacy bundle (intentionally — atomization scope): cinematic 4-layer parallax (per-pixel spherical projection × 4 depth layers is a per-pixel iteration loop, Plasma-Noise/Fractal class blocker for atomization until the graph compiler lands). Single-layer star field with UV drift reads as 'twinkling stars'; multi-layer revivable by duplicating the inner chain. Also dropped sliders: `depth` (was per-layer parallax scaling), `warmth` (per-star colour temperature — would need color_ramp wired through per-cell-hash bridge), `glow` (per-star halo extent — would need a second voronoi pass with wider gaussian).\n\nThe Array<CurvePoint> side-channel `stars` output from the legacy bundle is dropped (no current preset consumed it; restoring blocked on parked `wgsl_compute` infra).",
  "presetMetadata": {
    "id": "StarField",
    "displayName": "Star Field",
    "category": "Procedural",
    "oscPrefix": "starField",
    "available": true,
    "isLineBased": false,
    "params": [
      {
        "id": "scale",
        "name": "Scale",
        "min": 4.0,
        "max": 64.0,
        "defaultValue": 24.0,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F1",
        "oscSuffix": "scale"
      },
      {
        "id": "density",
        "name": "Density",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.6,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "density"
      },
      {
        "id": "size",
        "name": "Star Size",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.3,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "size"
      },
      {
        "id": "brightness",
        "name": "Brightness",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 4.0,
        "defaultValue": 1.5,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "brightness"
      },
      {
        "id": "drift_speed",
        "name": "Drift Speed",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.15,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "driftSpeed"
      },
      {
        "id": "drift_x",
        "name": "Drift X",
        "min": -1.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.3,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "driftX"
      },
      {
        "id": "drift_y",
        "name": "Drift Y",
        "min": -1.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.1,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "driftY"
      },
      {
        "id": "twinkle",
        "name": "Twinkle",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.6,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "twinkle"
      }
    ],
    "bindings": [
      { "id": "scale",       "label": "Scale",       "defaultValue": 24.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "cells", "param": "scale" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "scale",       "label": "Scale",       "defaultValue": 24.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "center_offset", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "density",     "label": "Density",     "defaultValue": 0.6,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "density_mask", "param": "low" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "size",        "label": "Star Size",   "defaultValue": 0.3,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "exponent_from_size", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "brightness",  "label": "Brightness",  "defaultValue": 1.5,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "final_brightness", "param": "scale" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "drift_speed", "label": "Drift Speed", "defaultValue": 0.15,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "drift_t", "param": "b" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "drift_x",     "label": "Drift X",     "defaultValue": 0.3,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "offset_x", "param": "scale" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "drift_y",     "label": "Drift Y",     "defaultValue": 0.1,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "offset_y", "param": "scale" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "twinkle",     "label": "Twinkle",     "defaultValue": 0.6,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "apply_twinkle", "param": "amount" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } }
    ],
    "paramAliases": [
      { "old": "depth", "new": "scale" }
    ],
    "skipMode": { "kind": "never" }
  },
  "nodes": [
    { "id": 0, "typeId": "system.generator_input", "handle": "input" },
    { "id": 1, "typeId": "system.final_output",    "handle": "final_output" },

    { "id": 2, "typeId": "node.math", "handle": "drift_t",
      "params": { "op": { "type": "Enum", "value": 2 }, "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "b": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.15 } } },

    { "id": 3, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "offset_x",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.3 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },
    { "id": 4, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "offset_y",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.1 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 5, "typeId": "node.voronoi_2d", "handle": "cells",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 24.0 }, "jitter": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }, "out_scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 6, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "invert_distance",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 7, "typeId": "node.power_texture", "handle": "spike",
      "params": { "exponent": { "type": "Float", "value": 22.0 } } },

    { "id": 8, "typeId": "node.channel_mix", "handle": "cell_hash_to_r",
      "params": {
        "row0": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0] },
        "row1": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0] },
        "row2": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0] },
        "row3": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0] }
      } },

    { "id": 9, "typeId": "node.smoothstep_texture", "handle": "density_mask",
      "params": { "low": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.6 }, "high": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 10, "typeId": "node.mix", "handle": "masked_stars",
      "params": { "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 4 }, "amount": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 11, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "freq_per_cell",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 3.5 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.5 } } },

    { "id": 12, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "phase_per_cell",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 6.2831853 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 13, "typeId": "node.trig_texture", "handle": "twinkle_sin",
      "params": { "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 }, "freq": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }, "phase": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 14, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "twinkle_to_unit",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.5 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.5 } } },

    { "id": 15, "typeId": "node.mix", "handle": "apply_twinkle",
      "params": { "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 4 }, "amount": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.6 } } },

    { "id": 16, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "final_brightness",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.5 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 17, "typeId": "node.channel_mix", "handle": "white_stars",
      "params": {
        "row0": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0] },
        "row1": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0] },
        "row2": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0] },
        "row3": { "type": "Vec4", "value": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0] }
      } },

    { "id": 18, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "center_offset",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 24.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": -0.5 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 19, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "exponent_from_size",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.3 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": -28.0 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 30.0 } } }
  ],
  "wires": [
    { "fromNode": 0, "fromPort": "time", "toNode": 2, "toPort": "a" },

    { "fromNode": 2, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 3, "toPort": "a" },
    { "fromNode": 2, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 4, "toPort": "a" },

    { "fromNode": 18, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 3, "toPort": "offset" },
    { "fromNode": 18, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 4, "toPort": "offset" },

    { "fromNode": 3, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 5, "toPort": "offset_x" },
    { "fromNode": 4, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 5, "toPort": "offset_y" },

    { "fromNode": 5, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 6,  "toPort": "in" },
    { "fromNode": 6, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 7,  "toPort": "in" },

    { "fromNode": 19, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 7, "toPort": "exponent" },

    { "fromNode": 7,  "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 17, "toPort": "source" },

    { "fromNode": 5, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 8,  "toPort": "source" },

    { "fromNode": 8, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 9,  "toPort": "in" },

    { "fromNode": 17, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 10, "toPort": "a" },
    { "fromNode": 9,  "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 10, "toPort": "b" },

    { "fromNode": 8, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 11, "toPort": "in" },
    { "fromNode": 8, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 12, "toPort": "in" },

    { "fromNode": 11, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 13, "toPort": "in" },
    { "fromNode": 0,  "fromPort": "time", "toNode": 13, "toPort": "freq" },
    { "fromNode": 12, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 13, "toPort": "phase_tex" },

    { "fromNode": 13, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 14, "toPort": "in" },

    { "fromNode": 10, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 15, "toPort": "a" },
    { "fromNode": 14, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 15, "toPort": "b" },

    { "fromNode": 15, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 16, "toPort": "in" },

    { "fromNode": 16, "fromPort": "out", "toNode": 1,  "toPort": "in" }
  ]
}
